STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Carlos ALVES, Defendant-Petitioner. C-296 September Term 2018
081169 Supreme Court of New Jersey. November 28, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002944-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
